          <script type="text/javascript">
           $(document).ready(function () {
            if ('False' == "True") {
                $("#ddlSort option[value='1']").remove();
            }
            var sortBy = '2';

            $("#ddlSort").val(sortBy);

            PopulateRelatedVideos('165', '1', 1, '6', sortBy, '60', '');

            $('#pagination').on('click', '.nonactive', function () {
                PopulateRelatedVideos('165', '1', $(this).attr('id').split('_')[1], '6', sortBy, '60', '');
            });

            $('#ddlSort').on('change', function () {
                sortBy = $(this).val();
                PopulateRelatedVideos('165', '1', '1', '6', sortBy, '60', '');
            });
        });

        function PopulateRelatedVideos(videoId, siteId, currentPage, videosPerPage, sortBy, searchLimit, tagId) {
            $.ajax({
                type: "POST",
                url: "/AjaxCallService.asmx/PopulateRelatedVideos",
                data: "{ 'videoId':'" + videoId + "','siteId':'" + siteId + "','currentPage':'" + currentPage + "','videosPerPage':'" + videosPerPage + "','sortBy':'" + sortBy + "','searchLimit':'" + searchLimit + "','tagId':'" + tagId +  "'}",
                contentType: "application/json; charset=utf-8",
                dataType: "json",
                success: function(msg) {
                    $('.videoList').html(msg.d);
                }
            });
            PopulateNumeric('10', '5', currentPage);
            return false;
        }
        function PopulateNumeric(totalPages, pagerWidth, currentPage) {
            $.ajax({
                type: "POST",
                url: "/AjaxCallService.asmx/PopulateNumeric",
                data: "{ 'totalPages':'" + totalPages + "','pagerWidth':'" + pagerWidth + "','currentPage':'" + currentPage + "'}",
                contentType: "application/json; charset=utf-8",
                dataType: "json",
                success: function (msg) {
                    $('.pager').html(msg.d);
                }
            });
        }
